/*                                                 */
/* Author : D.T.A.Brown                            */
/*                                                 */
/* History: 06-Aug-97: Created.                    */
/*          22-Aug-97: (ADH/DTAB) Integrated into  */
/*                     main browser code.          */
/*          25-Aug-97: (ADH) Definitions imported  */
/*                     from TBEvents.h.            */
